# Plan Mode — Mandatory Pre-Plan Gate

**Every time you enter Plan mode or are asked to plan a feature, fix, or refactor, you MUST complete ALL steps below in order. Do NOT skip any step. Do NOT write any implementation code or call CreatePlan until Step 6 is approved by the user.**

---

